column2: We maintain a very accurate registry of all military convoys on this planet. Recently, an analyst spotted something odd: a convoy that wasn't accounted for anywhere in our records. It's been regularly traveling along one of our standard logistical routes, and using our logistical comms, which is how it evaded detection for so long. Our signals intercepts tell us they're {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} drivers, so we have to assume they're smuggling right in our own backyard. We don't want to spook them with our own military comm chatter; we need an independent force to intercept and destroy them.

column2: A routine orbital survey of {TGT_SYSTEM.name} picked up coded transmissions from the surface. Our intelligence experts believe these transmissions come from a well-hidden {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} facility in this supposedly uninhabited system. Needless to say, {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} is not willing to tolerate secret military bases in this region. We need a mercenary company to intercept one of the supply caravans traveling to the secret base. Even if we can't find their facility, we can still starve them out.
column3: Обычная орбитальная разведка {TGT_SYSTEM.name} зафиксировала закодированные передачи с поверхности. Наши эксперты полагают, что эти сообщения поступают из хорошо замаскированного объекта {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} в этой, предположительно необитаемой системе. Излишне говорить, что {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} не желает мириться с секретными военными базами в этом регионе. Нам нужна команда наёмников, чтобы перехватить один из караванов с припасами, направляющихся на секретную базу. Даже если мы не сможем найти их объект, мы все равно сможем заморить их голодом.

column2: Guerrilla strikes against our facilities have increased, and our intel says {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} is bankrolling the guerrillas and providing logistical support in the form of small arms, explosives, and medical supplies. We need you to intercept the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} supply convoy and destroy it before it reaches the guerrilla forces.
column3: Количество атак партизан на наши объекты увеличилось, и наши разведданные говорят, о том, что {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} финансирует их и оказывает им материально-техническую поддержку в виде стрелкового оружия, взрывчатки и медикаментов. Нам нужно, чтобы вы перехватили конвой снабжения {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} и уничтожили его, прежде, чем он достигнет основных сил.

column2: Every month, {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} sends out another supply convoy loaded with military hardware and valuable electronics. They guard it heavily, so we're not asking you to hit the main force; no sense in throwing away good mercenaries. Instead we want you to pick off the tail end of the convoy. The cargo isn't as valuable as what they send out in the vanguard, but it won't be as heavily defended. Take the convoy out, and we'll send in our people to grab whatever's still intact. We don't really want to get shot at, so we'll pay a bonus if you take out all the defenders, as well.
column3: Каждый месяц {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} отправляет конвой, забитый под завязку военным оборудованием и электроникой. Его тщательно охраняют, поэтому мы не будем просить вступать с ними в бой; нет смысла разбрасываться хорошими наёмниками. Вместо этого мы хотим, чтобы вы отрезали хвост колонны. Груз в арьергарде не так ценен, как то, что они везут впереди, но он слабее защищен. Разбейте конвой и мы пришлем своих людей для сбора груза. Нам бы не хотелось, чтобы по нам стреляли, поэтому за полное уничтожение сил защиты мы заплатим сверх суммы контракта.

column2: Somehow we've let {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} get their hands on one of our less reliable suppliers. It only took them a few days to break her, and now she's ready to spill all kinds of secrets in court. That isn't in our best interests, and since you're talking to us, it's not in yours, either. We'd like to do a little bit of witness tampering, of the fatal variety. She's being transported to a secure facility by ground vehicle. column2: Our sources on the planet have alerted us to a convoy of vehicles being transferred to an otherwise undefended military base. If we act quickly, we can destroy that convoy before it has a chance to reinforce the base. Normally we wouldn't be concerned about a simple vehicle convoy, but {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} intelligence operatives report that one of the vehicles is a fully operational Schrek PPC carrier. That's not a threat we can afford to ignore. We need you to eliminate that convoy before they make it to their base.

column2: The target we'd like your people to eliminate is a notorious killer-for-hire who goes by the name 'The Professional'. They're currently under contract with {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName}, and they've been spotted here on {TGT_SYSTEM.name}, which is extremely concerning for our interests. This mercenary is cagey and cautious and will attempt escape at any indication that they're overmatched. We'd like you to land a low-tonnage lance to engage them, to give them a false sense of security, and then eliminate them before they can escape. We're prepared to offer very generous salvage terms.

column2: Commander, this mission should be simple. A {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} noble is participating in a patrol, as a show of support for the troops. She's insisted on using her ancestral family 'Mech, which is a Cicada CDA-2A. This should make eliminating her quite easy. Recognizing the danger, her handlers have sent along an extremely heavy supporting lance. If you're quick, and aggressive, you should be able to destroy her little Cicada before her escorts can react.
column3: Командир, эта миссия должна быть легче лёгкого. Аристократка из {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} участвует в патрулировании в знак поддержки своих войск. Она настояла на пилотировании меха ее предков - «Цикада» CDA-2A. Это должно упростить ее устранение. Осознавая всю опасность, ее посредники прислали с ней тяжелое копье поддержки. Если сделать всё быстро и агрессивно, вы сможете уничтожить ее «Цикаду» до того, как ее эскорт успеет среагировать.

column2: An elite MechWarrior has been deployed to take command of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces in this system. We need a skilled mercenary force to remove this MechWarrior before they reach their command, while they're only lightly escorted. Every downed 'Mech will help our cause, so there will be a bonus for complete destruction of the target's supporting forces. Additionally, the MechWarrior's command may send out an escort unit to meet them; expect enemy reinforcements once you engage.
column3: Элитный мехвоин вызван для управления силами {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} в этой системе. Нам нужны опытные наемники, чтобы убрать его до того, как он доберётся до основных сил, пока его сопровождает лишь лёгкий эскорт. Каждый уничтоженный мех поможет нашему делу, поэтому мы заплатим премию за полное уничтожение всех отрядов. Кроме того, вражеское командование может послать дополнительные силы, ожидайте подкреплений.

column2: For months, we've had trouble with people here in {TGT_SYSTEM.name} being riled up by talk of insurrection, rebellion, independence. Based on top {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} analysts' reports, we believe there's a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} propagandist in the area, stirring up discontent. We've set up a security net to capture her. But we can't cover every possible exit from our net and could use an extra Lance of 'Mechs. If she tries to slip through your assigned territory, turn her unit to slag.

column2: It's reached a point where we can no longer operate in {TGT_SYSTEM.name}, Commander, and it's all thanks to a particular {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} MechWarrior tasked with tracking down our activities in this region. We're tired of letting him pick the time and place of battle, so we'd like you to give him a little surprise visit while he's on patrol. He'll be defended and given his paranoia he'll probably have backup waiting nearby, so watch for an ambush.
column3: Командир, дела обстоят так, что мы больше не можем проводить наши операции в {TGT_SYSTEM.name} и всё это благодаря одному конкретному мехвоину {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, который отслеживает всю нашу деятельность в этом регионе. Нам надоело позволять ему выбирать место и время битвы, поэтому мы бы хотели, чтобы вы нанесли ему визит, пока он в патруле. Парень - параноик, поэтому его всегда сопровождает отряд бойцов, а то и два. Опасайтесь засады.

column2: Our spies report that a veteran {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} MechWarrior from the Succession Wars retired to this system, and {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.ShortName} would very much like to keep him retired. Permanently if possible. We've been monitoring a DropShip in orbit around the planet, and believe that they're preparing for a pickup. We need you to drop and intercept this MechWarrior before he can be reactivated. He's likely in a fairly heavy 'Mech, so be careful when you engage him.

A {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} surveillance team picked up {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} signals from the surface of {TGT_SYSTEM.Name} that correspond to a very heavy 'Mech running through a test-fire sequence. column2: A {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} patrol detected unexpected signals here in {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}, and we'd like you to investigate. Analysis suggests that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} has reactivated an abandoned factory on the planet's surface. We don't know what this particular facility was used for, but given the effort they're sinking into this, it must be valuable. We want it.
column3: Патруль {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} обнаружил необычные сигналы здесь, на {TGT_SYSTEM.Name} и мы просим вас провести расследование. Анализ показывает, что {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} восстановили заброшенный завод на поверхности планеты. Мы не знаем для чего использовался этот конкретный объект, но, учитывая усилия, которые они приложили, он должен быть очень ценен. И мы хотим его себе.

column2: A {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} family lost a large area of land on {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}, thanks to dubious legal maneuvering by {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} agents. This land includes an important ancestral military base. We need this base taken back from {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName} and held until this can be sorted out.
column3: Один знатный род из фракции {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} лишился большого участка земли на планете {TGT_SYSTEM.Name} из-за махинаций юристов фракции {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}. На этом участке располагается важная военная база этого знатного рода. Вам поручается отбить эту базу у войск {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName} и удерживать её, пока с этими махинациями не разберутся.

column2: We've been monitoring communications traffic on {TGT_SYSTEM.name}, and discerned a pattern. There's a well-defended {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} base that we suspect of being a secure data storage facility. We'd like your team to land, capture the base, and take a complete image of the contents of their databases. Once the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces realize what we're doing, they'll launch a counteroffensive, so we'll need you to stay in the field until the download is complete.

column2: Data Piracy
column3: Пиратство данных

column2: Commander, once you reach the base I'll be able to start extracting the data. It shouldn't take very long; I can't imagine their data security is very sophisticated.
column3: Командир, как только вы доберетесь до базы, я смогу начать извлекать данные. Это не займет много времени; Я не могу представить, чтобы их безопасность данных была очень сложной.

column2: Physical security, on the other hand... I'm seeing what looks like turrets around the facility.
column3: Physical security, on the other hand... I'm seeing what looks like turrets around the facility.

column2: We should get eyes on that base before we charge in shooting. This should be a good vantage point.
column3: We should get eyes on that base before we charge in shooting. This should be a good vantage point.

column2: Aaaand... done. That's all the data, Commander. I'm ready for extraction.
column3: Иии... готово. Это все данные, командир. Можно собираться и улетать.

column2: Damn! Commander, I didn't get the download.
column3: Черт! Командир, мне не удалось скачать.

column2: Bogeys on sensors!
column3: Новые точки на радаре!

column2: Oh hey, just like I said. Turrets. Watch yourself, Commander.
column3: Oh hey, just like I said. Turrets. Watch yourself, Commander.

column2: There's the facility, Commander. That's-- There weren't supposed to be any units in the base, Commander.
column3: There's the facility, Commander. That's-- There weren't supposed to be any units in the base, Commander.

column2: Sounds like our employers have their own data security problems.
column3: Sounds like our employers have their own data security problems.

column3: Uh, folks? I just spotted more engine signatures -- 'Mechs powering up. More bad guys are on their way to you, boss.

column2: Just like that time on Axylus, hm? Don't worry; I work well under pressure.
column3: Just like that time on Axylus, hm? Don't worry; I work well under pressure.

column2: Commander, we're preparing a series of operations on {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. However, before we can begin, we need a secure lodgement to bring military units and supplies down to the surface. We've identified a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} military facility that will be ideal for our purposes. We need you to land a strike force, capture the facility, and hold it until we can bring down our people to secure the location. Because this operation is covert and on an extremely tight schedule, you'll be inserting with no topographical intel.
column3: Командир, мы готовим серию операций на {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. Однако прежде, чем мы сможем начать, нам нужна надёжная база, чтобы развернуть вооруженные силы и снабжение. Мы определили военный объект {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, который идеально подходит для наших целей. Нам нужно, чтобы вы высадили ударную группу, захватили объект и удерживали его, пока мы подтягиваем наших людей, чтобы обезопасить зону. Поскольку эта операция является скрытой и сжатой по срокам, вам придется высаживаться без данных топографической разведки.

This facility is a key supplier for local {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} forces, and taking it from them will significantly damage their efforts against us. We'd like you to drop in, take the depot, and hold out against any enemy reinforcements.

column2: Fifteen years ago we lost track of a facility here on {TGT_SYSTEM.name}, and {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} intelligence believed it had been permanently shut down. A month ago, an orbiting spy satellite picked up signs that the facility had been brought back online. Our current guess is that a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} team was dispatched to bring the base back up to operational capacity. We'd rather not have sensitive radar backed by armed turrets and flak batteries aimed at the skies of {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. We'd like you to clear their team out and hold the facility while our own people land to scour it for useful intel.

We'd rather not have sensitive radar backed by armed turrets and flak batteries aimed at the skies of {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. column2: We've learned that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} here in {TGT_SYSTEM.name} has been busy working on a new water filtration technology, which is both extremely valuable and likely to shift the balance of power in the region by opening up more worlds for colonization. We've discovered where they're working on the latest prototype. We know that they are monitoring the location of our own 'Mechs in the area, so we need a mercenary lance to make the vanguard assault and catch them by surprise. We'll then take over the facility with {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} forces.

column2: Apparently {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} controls a network of transports and warehouses in the {TGT_SYSTEM.name} system, moving mostly mundane merchandise but also a very few highly valuable goods. Our clandestine research efforts have acquired the latest shipping manifests and identified an opportunity for a swift, profitable strike at a key shipping hub. If timed properly, your Mechs can attack quickly and pave the way for a {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} extraction team to empty the warehouse of its contents.
column3: По всей видимости {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} имеет транспортную сеть в системе {TGT_SYSTEM.name} с большим числом складов, которая занимается перевозкой по-большей части обычных, но иногда и весьма редких товаров. Наша агентурная сеть смогла заполучить новые накладные на грузы и выявила окно для быстрого и прибыльного налёта на их ключевой погрузочный узел. Вам необходимо в точно рассчитанное время высадиться и расчистить путь для команды {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name}, которые избавят склады от их содержимого.

column2: We've got a developing situation, Commander, and we need immediate aid from a reliable mercenary company. A covert {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} team was investigating reports of a cache of bioweapons on an otherwise abandoned world. We've tracked down four of these caches in the Periphery over the last 20 years, and disposed of them safely. The team was about to signal for an extraction when their signal went dead. We have reason to believe that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces have taken control of the cache site, and eliminated our covert team. We need you to take that site and signal our disposal team.
column3: We've got a developing situation, Commander, and we need immediate aid from a reliable mercenary company. column2: So all we gotta do is just walk in there and stand around? This job sounds like bullshit to me. I wanna learn how to shoot, not stand around!
column3: So all we gotta do is just walk in there and stand around? This job sounds like bullshit to me. I wanna learn how to shoot, not stand around!

column2: I don't know, the mission sounds good to me. I need more practice driving this thing, anyway.
column3: I don't know, the mission sounds good to me. I need more practice driving this thing, anyway.

column2: Let's confirm the base is undefended. Commander, move up to this location and you should be able to get eyes on the base.
column3: Let's confirm the base is undefended. Commander, move up to this location and you should be able to get eyes on the base.

column2: Can we blow up some of the buildings?
column3: А можно сломать парочку домиков?

column2: Well... that certainly was an experience. Darius, I think we should get hazard pay for this kind of mission.
column3: Well... that certainly was an experience. Darius, I think we should get hazard pay for this kind of mission.

column2: Stow it, Meyer. It all worked out fine, and we get paid.
column3: Stow it, Meyer. It all worked out fine, and we get paid.

column2: I think these kids could use some more time on the practice range.
column3: I think these kids could use some more time on the practice range.

column2: Bogeys on sensors!
column3: Новые точки на радаре!

column2: [GENERIC VO] Area is not clear, Commander. Eliminate the hostiles before continuing to the next Objective.
column3: [GENERIC VO] Командир, в вашем районе замечены вражеские силы. Придётся сначала разобраться с ними.

column2: [GENERIC VO] Sensors are clear, proceed to the next objective.
column3: [GENERIC VO] На сенсорах чисто, переходите к следующей цели.

column2: That's it, Commander. Our employer is sending in the cavalry. Good work.
column3: That's it, Commander. Our employer is sending in the cavalry. Good work.

column2: Aww, really? Come on, I want more targets!
column3: Ой, серьёзно? Да ладно, давайте ещё!

column2: Hey, Darius? Didn't they say the base was decommissioned?
column3: Hey, Darius? Didn't they say the base was decommissioned?

column2: Yes. Why, do you have something?
column3: Yes. Why, do you have something?

column2: Those are turrets, boss, and they're not offline. They're powered up and pinging me and the Leopard.
column3: Those are turrets, boss, and they're not offline. They're powered up and pinging me and the Leopard.

column2: T-turrets? And they're going to shoot at us? Wait, I thought this was-
column3: T-turrets? And they're going to shoot at us? Wait, I thought this was-

column2: HELL yeah! Live fire, baby!
column3: Да, чёрт возьми! Зажигай!

column2: There's the base up ahead. It looks empty...
column3: There's the base up ahead. It looks empty...

column2: That sucks. Can I shoot some of the buildings anyway?
column3: That sucks. Can I shoot some of the buildings anyway?

column2: Huh. I'm picking up engine signatures, boss. Reinforcements, and they're headed your way.
column3: Huh. I'm picking up engine signatures, boss. Reinforcements, and they're headed your way.

column2: Oh shit, oh shit, I don't want to die-
column3: Oh shit, oh shit, I don't want to die-

column2: Get your lance into that base, Commander, and hold out till our employer can get some more people on the ground.
column3: Get your lance into that base, Commander, and hold out till our employer can get some more people on the ground.

column2: This seems like a mission where afterwards we'll say 'It was supposed to be undefended!', Commander. Be prepared.
column3: This seems like a mission where afterwards we'll say 'It was supposed to be undefended!', Commander. Be prepared.

column3: We'll rendezvous with them at this location, and then provide an escort.

column2: These aren't fighters, Commander. They'll die under any serious assault. So be careful.
column3: These aren't fighters, Commander. They'll die under any serious assault. So be careful.

column2: The survivors of the failed colony are safely away, Commander. Good job.
column3: The survivors of the failed colony are safely away, Commander. Good job.

column3: This is a disaster. We need to review the mission logs and see what went wrong.

column3: Командир, противник высадил подкрепления и они уже близко, готовьтесь к встрече.

column3: More contacts on the sensors, Commander. Looks like {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} *really* doesn't want these colonists making it out of here.

column2: And they are away! The convoy is safely out of the AO. Good work, Commander. Now get your remaining forces to the second evac zone for extraction there.
column3: Ну вот и все! Конвой благополучно покинул зону операции. Хорошая работа, командир. Теперь направьте оставшиеся силы во вторую зону эвакуации, пора уходить отсюда.

column2: My guess is that there was a credible threat made on the colony, and that's why they're pulling out. Expect fighting, Commander.
column3: My guess is that there was a credible threat made on the colony, and that's why they're pulling out. Expect fighting, Commander.

column2: Less than an hour ago, we lost contact with a covert team tasked with infiltrating a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} facility. The only reason for them not to respond is if their operation was blown, by discovery or counterintelligence. The research materials they were meant to collect are extremely important, and we can't afford to lose them. We need you to make a rapid and immediate deployment to the the facility, and get our people and their cargo to safety.
column3: Менее часа назад мы потеряли связь с группой специального назначения, которой было поручено проникнуть на объект {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}. Их молчание можно расценивать как провал операции, их либо обнаружили, либо это старается контрразведка. Исследовательские материалы, которые они должны были собрать, чрезвычайно важны и мы не можем позволить себе их потерять. Необходимо, чтобы вы быстро и без промедлений прибыли на объект и переправили наших людей и их груз в безопасное место.

column2: Less than an hour ago, we lost contact with a covert team tasked with infiltrating a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} facility. The only reason for them not to respond is if their operation was blown, by discovery or counterintelligence. The research materials they were meant to collect are extremely important, and we can't afford to lose them. We need you to make a rapid and immediate deployment to the the facility, and get our people and their cargo to safety.

column2: A {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} DropShip went down on this empty rock, and shortly thereafter we detected a distress signal from the surface. By the time we arrived, the crew had been taken captive by a heavily armed {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} force. We don't have an in-system military presence large enough to mount a hostage rescue mission, so we're looking for a competent mercenary company to do it. We need you to reach the facility where the crew is being held, destroy the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} units guarding them, and escort them to safety.
column3: Дропшип {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} упал на эту пустую скалу, и вскоре после этого мы обнаружили сигнал бедствия с поверхности. К тому времени, как мы прибыли, экипаж был захвачен хорошо вооруженными силами {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}. У нас недостаточно сил в системе, чтобы организовать операцию по спасению заложников, поэтому мы ищем компетентную компанию наемников . Нам нужно, достигли объекта, где содержаться наши люди, уничтожьте охраняющих их подразделения {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} и сопроводите их в безопасное место.

column2: A {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} politician is looking for an armed escort to guide him safely to a diplomatic summit. We can assure you that any accusations of bribery and corruption are completely unfounded. His {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} enemies are simply stirring up the common people against him.
column3: Политик из {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} ищет вооруженный эскорт, чтобы провести его на дипломатическое собрание. Мы можем вас заверить, что любые обвинения во взяточничестве и коррупции полностью безосновательны. Его враги из {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} просто настраивают против него простых людей.

column2: A long-time enemy of {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} has unexpectedly turned herself into local authorities, and will now be extradited to another system for trial. However, {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} does not want to see her testify, and will try to stop her from leaving the planet. We've secured a convoy of armored vehicles to transport the criminal, but we need the extra fire-power of your 'Mechs to guarantee a safe path to the evacuation zone.
column3: Давний враг из {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} неожиданно сдался местным властям. Теперь его отправят в другую систему для суда. Однако {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} не хотят дожидаться показаний в суде - они попытаются помешать покинуть планету. М располагаем конвоем бронетехники для перевозки преступника, но нам понадобится дополнительная огневая мощь ваших мехов, чтобы гарантировать безопасный путь к зоне эвакуации.

column2: We're looking for a mercenary company with a reputation for discretion. While his convoy is armed and armored, he suspects that his enemies have hired mercenaries of their own to interdict this shipment.

We have arranged for a garrison force to be moved into place, but we need mercenaries to protect the factory until our forces arrive.

column2: Hold the base, keep the buildings upright, and eliminate any threats. Oliveira out.

column2: A {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} industrial lab is at a critical juncture in its R&D program. Any disruption would set us back a decade. {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} on {TGT_SYSTEM.name} has discovered this, and they've already interdicted the first lance of 'Mechs that were sent to defend the facility. We need mercenaries to step in and buy the time necessary for further reinforcements to arrive.
column3: Промышленная лаборатория {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} находится на финальном этапе своей программы исследований и разработок. Любой сбой отбросит нас лет на десять назад. {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} на {TGT_SYSTEM.name} обнаружили это и уже перехватили первое копье мехов, посланных для защиты объекта. Нам нужны наёмники, чтобы выиграть время, необходимое для прибытия подкреплений.

column2: As part of a propaganda effort, we've been operating a secret holo-vid broadcasting facility on {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. The clearest sign that our efforts are working is that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} agents have spent months searching for the facility. Unfortunately, they've succeeded, and are launching an assault on what they believe to be an undefended installation. While our personnel prepare for evacuation and destroy all the files and documents, we need a team of mercenaries to hold off {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces.
column3: В целях пропаганды мы запустили секретную станцию трансляции голо-видео в системе {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. Агенты {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} месяцами ищут наш объект, это явный показатель того, что наши усилия не прошли даром. К сожалению, они преуспели и начинают наступление на якобы незащищенное сооружение. Пока наш персонал готовится к эвакуации и уничтожает все файлы и документы, нам нужна команда наемников, чтобы сдержать силы {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}.

column2: Commander, half the base is in flames! If we lose another building, our employer's going to pull the plug on this contract.
column3: Командир, половина базы в руинах! Если мы потеряем еще одно строение, наш работодатель разорвёт контракт.

column2: Mercenary Commander, we've received word of the assault on your position. Reinforcements are incoming, they are about halfway there. Maintain position and you will be relieved and reinforced shortly.
column3: Командующий наёмниками, мы получили известие о штурме вашей позиции. Наши подкрепления скоро будут, они примерно на полпути. Держитесь там.

column3: Командир, на этой прогулке наниматель предоставит нам дополнительную поддержку.

column3: They have point defenses set up around the base, they are however offline.

column3: We have a friendly convoy with engineers who are eager to get at those defenses, so they can bring them online.

column3: Доставьте их к генераторам в целости и мы сможем усилить нашу оборону этими турелями. Удачи!

column2: A few hours ago, some enterprising lads from our organization planetside were able to seize control of a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} research facility. They maybe hadn't thought their entire plan through, so right now there's a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} strike force on the way to level the base before our boys can download any valuable data. We need you to cover them while they finish up and escape.
column3: Несколько часов назад наши предприимчивые ребята смогли захватить научную лабораторию {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}. Возможно они не до конца всё продумали, так как в этот момент ударный отряд {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} направляется туда с целью сровнять эту лабораторию с землей до того, как парни смогут скачать важную информацию. Вы нужны нам, чтобы прикрыть ребят, пока они не закончат и не покинут объект.

column2: Somehow, the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} authorities have discovered one of our storehouses. If it were just drugs or stolen goods, we'd let them seize it and write it off as a loss. But it's a weapons stockpile, and those damn things are hard to move from one system to another. We'd like you to protect our guns while our people load them onto transports and we evacuate them.

column2: We've got a facility down on {TGT_SYSTEM.Name} where we store valuable hardware before loading it aboard our DropShips for transport out of the system. Unfortunately, the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} authorities have discovered our facility, and they're not interested in making any kind of accommodation that lets us get our goods off-planet. We need you to defend the place while we load our valuables up for evacuation.

Unfortunately, the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} authorities have discovered our facility, and they're not interested in making any kind of accommodation that lets us get our goods off-planet. We need you to defend the place while we load our valuables up for evacuation.

column2: Professional Ethics
column3: Professional Ethics

column2: The manufacturing facility is just up ahead. Meyer, any sign of our polite opposition?
column3: The manufacturing facility is just up ahead. Meyer, any sign of our polite opposition?

column2: I'm seeing... uh, I'm seeing a lot of engine signatures out there, XO.
column3: I'm seeing... uh, I'm seeing a lot of engine signatures out there, XO.

column2: I gave you plenty of time to prepare. Did you think I wouldn't prepare as well?
column3: I gave you plenty of time to prepare. Did you think I wouldn't prepare as well?

column2: I don't get it. What's the point of this?
column3: I don't get it. What's the point of this?

column2: To prove which of us is better: your whole company... or me.
column3: To prove which of us is better: your whole company... or me.

column2: I suppose this means we're the better mercenaries, though I'm not sure why we needed to know that.
column3: I suppose this means we're the better mercenaries, though I'm not sure why we needed to know that.

column2: Indeed. One of these days I'll have to take the field against you personally.
column3: Indeed. One of these days I'll have to take the field against you personally.

column2: That transmission is coming from a relay in orbit. They weren't even here, just remote piloting a 'Mech.
column3: That transmission is coming from a relay in orbit. They weren't even here, just remote piloting a 'Mech.

column2: What a damn disaster. Let's debrief back in orbit.
column3: What a damn disaster. Let's debrief back in orbit.

column2: Argo, my engineers are powering the turrets up now. The APCs will scatter and provide support.
column3: Арго, сейчас мои инженеры активируют турели. БТРы рассредоточатся и окажут поддержку.

column2: Roger, local command. Commander, looks like we have a few more guns on our side.
column3: Roger, local command. Commander, looks like we have a few more guns on our side.

column2: My people only have one more building left to destroy. You're not going to at least try and make this a challenge for me?
column3: My people only have one more building left to destroy. You're not going to at least try and make this a challenge for me?

column2: Mercenary Commander, we've received word of the assault on your position. Reinforcements are incoming, they are about halfway there. Maintain position and you will be relieved and reinforced shortly.

column2: Argo, this is {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} local command. Our turrets have been disabled by sabotage.

column2: We have an extremely odd assignment for you. We have a manufacturing facility on the planet below, and we've been aware that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces have been scouting in the area. We've expected them to make a move, but we didn't expect them to... send us a warning beforehand? Apparently they've hired a mercenary who contacted us to let us know when the attack would be, because, and I'm quoting, \"professional ethics.\" We have no idea what that means.
column3: We have an extremely odd assignment for you. We have a manufacturing facility on the planet below, and we've been aware that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} forces have been scouting in the area. We've expected them to make a move, but we didn't expect them to... send us a warning beforehand? Apparently they've hired a mercenary who contacted us to let us know when the attack would be, because, and I'm quoting, "professional ethics." We have no idea what that means.

column2: Titan Attack

column2: Meyer, are you picking up that assault 'Mech they said would be here?

column2: No, I'm-- wait, there it is. Shit, that's big. How the hell are we supposed to keep that from blowing shit up?
column3: No, I'm-- wait, there it is. Shit, that's big. How the hell are we supposed to keep that from blowing shit up?

column2: Engage it and keep it firing at our people, instead of the buildings.

column2: I just wanna go on the record here: that's a terrible plan, and you're going to break my 'Mechs.

column2: I'm not happy with this, boss. It could have been worse, but let's not take contracts where you use my 'Mechs as punching bags?

column2: We have a very ambitious target in mind for you: a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} logistical base. Thousands of tons of armor, ammunition, 'Mech parts, and personnel pass through this facility every day, all on its way to front-line fighting units. A strike at this base will seriously hinder the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces, possibly even turning the tide of battle completely against them. It will be well-defended, and as soon as the assault begins the enemy will scramble reinforcements.

Earlier today, our facility here on {TGT_SYSTEM.name} received what they believed was a normal data transmission. It was badly garbled, and when they requested it be re-sent, they got no response. Shortly thereafter the base systems began to malfunction, and then we lost contact with both the base and the synchronous satellites covering that region. We'd like you to investigate the facility.

We've lost a base to {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, and believe {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} personnel are being interrogated even now. We can't allow those people to spill their secrets, but it would look bad if we were seen to destroy our own base. We need deniability. We need you to level the base, particularly the storage and communications facilities. We'd appreciate it if you ensured there were no living witnesses, and will pay a bonus if you wipe out all the opposition.

Стратегически, этот завод расположен очень неудобно для захвата, поэтому нам нужно, чтобы вы его уничтожили. Если действовать быстро, то вы справитесь со всем ещё до того, как первый мех сойдёт с конвеера. Если вы всё же встретите новых мехов, их, конечно, следует превратить обратно в металлолом.

Мы просто обязаны на это ответить, уничтожив один из их заводов по производству боеприпасов в системе {TGT_SYSTEM.name}.

column2: A few months ago, we intercepted a number of highly encrypted transmissions originating from the planet, none of which we've been able to decrypt and read. We suspected that the transmissions came from a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} black site, and sent an operative to infiltrate and steal the decryption key. They reported in requesting immediate emergency extraction. We'd like you to recover the key, and the operative if they're still alive.
column3: Несколько месяцев назад мы перехватили несколько сильно зашифрованных передач, исходящих с этой планеты. Ни одну из них так и не удалось расшифровать и прочитать. Мы заподозрили, что передачи пришли из секретной базы {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} и отправили туда оперативника, чтобы проникнуть и украсть ключ дешифровки. Сейчас он запрашивает экстренную эвакуацию. Мы бы хотели, чтобы вы вернули и ключ и оперативника, если он еще жив.

column2: Commander, we perform a substantial amount of scientific research here in {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces have been sabotaging our research stations, stretching our defenses thin. We've just learned that their ultimate target is a key scientist in our weapons development program. They've launched an assault that we believe is intended to capture her. We need you to reach the facility where she's stationed and extract her to safety.
column3: На планете {TGT_SYSTEM.Name} проводится значительное число наших научных исследований. К сожалению, из-за постоянных нападений и саботажа со стороны {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} наша защита сильно ослабла. Разведка недавно выяснила, что настоящей целью нападений является одна из ведущих учёных, задействованных в одном из проектов по разработке оружия. Также нам стало известно, что противник собирается начать штурм лаборатории, в которой она работает, с целью её захвата. Необходимо, чтобы ваш отряд высадился в данном районе как можно скорее и эвакуировал её в безопасное место.

column2: Carrier
column3: Орудийная платформа

column2: You want to do what with my 'Mechs?
column3: You want to do what with my 'Mechs?

column2: Told you so.
column3: Told you so.

column2: Yang, they will be perfectly safe. We'll scrub the command software once they're onboard the Leopard, and the virus won't even get near the Argo or the 'Mech Bay.
column3: Yang, they will be perfectly safe. We'll scrub the command software once they're onboard the Leopard, and the virus won't even get near the Argo or the 'Mech Bay.

column2: Goddamn right we will.
column3: Goddamn right we will.

column2: Commander, you'll need to move within range of the facility to pick up the virus signal. Order a 'Mech into this region and it should download automatically.
column3: Commander, you'll need to move within range of the facility to pick up the virus signal. Order a 'Mech into this region and it should download automatically.

column2: Protect the infected unit until you reach the extraction LZ, where Sumire will pick you up. Good luck, Commander.
column3: Protect the infected unit until you reach the extraction LZ, where Sumire will pick you up. Good luck, Commander.

column2: We've transferred the corrupted command software to storage.
column3: We've transferred the corrupted command software to storage.

column2: Good! Now wipe that damn thing before it gets into the Leopard!
column3: Good! Now wipe that damn thing before it gets into the Leopard!

column2: I told you this was a bad idea. Before you bring that thing back onto the Argo I want you to torch its computers.
column3: I told you this was a bad idea. Before you bring that thing back onto the Argo I want you to torch its computers.

column2: All the data coming from your unit just went bonkers, Commander. I'm just seeing static from its feed up here.
column3: All the data coming from your unit just went bonkers, Commander. I'm just seeing static from its feed up here.

column2: You don't need instruments to follow a giant titanium BattleMech; just eyeball it, Meyer. Commander, protect that unit and get it out of there.
column3: You don't need instruments to follow a giant titanium BattleMech; just eyeball it, Meyer. Commander, protect that unit and get it out of there.

column3: [GENERIC VO] Вторая цель у нас, командир.

column2: We've discovered a facility where {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} researchers have developed a new computer virus that targets the control mechanisms of our 'Mechs. We can't build an effective defense against this virus without a sample of its code to work with. We need you to get one of your 'Mechs within range of the research facility and download the virus into its systems. Then extract the infected carrier 'Mech so we can analyze the virus.
column3: We've discovered a facility where {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} researchers have developed a new computer virus that targets the control mechanisms of our 'Mechs. We can't build an effective defense against this virus without a sample of its code to work with. We need you to get one of your 'Mechs within range of the research facility and download the virus into its systems. Then extract the infected carrier 'Mech so we can analyze the virus.

column2: Corporate Secrets
column3: У корпорации есть свои секреты

column2: This is the region where the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} facility is located.
column3: Вот этот регион, где расположен объект {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}.

column2: There it is. Move up and occupy the facility, Commander.
column3: Вот оно. Выдвигайтесь и зачистите объект, командир.

column2: Once it's secure, get the rogue scientist into one of your 'Mechs, and head for the marked evac zone.
column3: Как только зона будет безопасна, садите учёную шпионку в любой мех и направляйтесь в отмеченную зону эвакуации.

column2: Sumire will be waiting for your signal to pick you up. Best of luck, Commander.
column3: Сумир будет ждать сигнала, чтобы подобрать вас. Удачи, командир.

column2: Excellent work, commander. The wayward {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} scientist is on her way home.
column3: Отличная работа, командир. Опальная мадам едет домой, в {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name}.

column2: Disappointing, Commander. I'll let our employers know that they might want to go back to the negotiating table.
column3: Как же так, командир. Видимо придётся предложить нашим работодателям всё же рассмотреть вариант с переговорами.

column2: You're in the right area. Hold position and force the scientist to board one of the Mechs.
column3: Вы пришли по адресу. Удерживайте позиции и заставьте ученую выйти.

column2: [GENERIC VO] The asset is sustaining damage, Commander!
column3: [GENERIC VO] Груз получает повреждения, командир!

column3: [GENERIC VO] Груз номер два под огнём, командир!

column3: [GENERIC VO] Посылка доставлена, командир. Хорошая работа.

column2: [GENERIC VO] The secondary asset has been recovered, Commander.
column3: [GENERIC VO] Груз номер два у нас, командир.

column2: That's it, the Mech recovering our Secondary Target is scrapped. That objective is failed. Focus on getting the scientist to safety.
column3: Ну всё, груз номер два для нас потерян. Сконцентрируйтесь на том, чтобы доставить ученую в безопасное место.

column2: I think I've lost track of how many layers of betrayal this represents. Is this a quadruple-cross? This must be some scientist.
column3: Кажется я сбился со счёту, сколько там слоев предательства? Это уже не двойная игра, а типо... четверная? Эта учёная тот ещё фрукт.

column3: Обезопасьте место, чтобы подобрать учёного

column2: A scientist for a {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} conglomerate has turned industrial spy for a rival corporation from {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName}. She was privy to numerous industrial secrets that we would prefer not to fall into our competitor's hands. The {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} leadership has offered to sell her back, but we intend to use the false hope of negotiations to buy you time to extract the scientist through more proactive means.
column3: Ученая {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} оказалась шпионом конкурирующей корпорации из {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName}. Она знает множество промышленных секретов, которые мы предпочли бы не передавать в руки наших соперников. Руководство {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} предложило деньги за её возвращение, но мы намерены использовать ложные переговоры, чтобы выиграть для вас время перевезти учёного в безопасное место.

Payment will be issued when you deliver our VIP alive and in one piece.

A local group of sympathizers on {TGT_SYSTEM.name} recently picked up a garbled message from the scion indicating that she's being held in a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} facility there. Our intel failed to trace her to {TGT_SYSTEM.name}, so any loyal mechs are several jumps away. We need your help to extract her.

column2: A {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} philanthropist is a patron of the arts here in {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. A favored painter has been accused of heresy by the system's religious police. These zealots are propped up by foreign {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} agents. He'll be extradited to face trial and likely execution in {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} territory. We can't allow that to happen, but we don't want to incur reprisal from the religious leaders. That's where you come in. Locate the painter, rescue him and, at the personal request of the patron, recover the painting that started this whole mess.
column3: Филантроп из {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} покровительствует местному искусству здесь, на {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. Любимый художник был обвинен в ереси религиозной полицией системы. Этих фанатиков поддерживают иностранные агенты {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}. Он будет отдан под суд и, вероятно, казнён на территории {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}. Мы не можем этого допустить, но мы также не хотим навлечь на себя репрессии со стороны религиозных лидеров. Вот тут-то вы и вступите в дело. Найдите художника, спасите его и, по личной просьбе покровителя, верните картину из-за которой всё это началось.

column2: A {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} defector has given us an extremely interesting and time-sensitive piece of information, and we need a fast response. Before joining our side, this defector worked at a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} facility on this planet. She claims she was responsible for extracting data from a device that sounds, from her descriptions, very much like a Star League era memory core. We don't know what data is on it, but {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName} cannot be allowed to keep it.
column3: Перебежчик {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} выдал нам крайне интересную инофрмацию срочного характера, поэтому действовать надо быстро. До перехода к нам он работал на предприятии {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName} на этой планете. Он утверждает, что отвечал за процесс извлечения данных из устройства, по описанию очень напоминающее банк данных Звёздной Лиги. Мы понятия не имеем, какие данные там записаны, но они не должны оставаться в грязных руках {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName}.

column2: A high tonnage {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance will shortly make planetfall, at the behest of a group of petty nobles and commercial interests. Intel suggests this is the vanguard of a larger force of conventional tanks and infantry, and they're scouting the region for a suitable landing site. We need a competent mercenary company to intercept the 'Mechs and stop the invasion before it gets underway. If their planet-side allies send any support, you are to wipe them out as well.
column3: Тяжелое копьё {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} вскоре совершит посадку на эту планету по воле группы мелких дворян и их коммерческих интересов. Разведка предполагает, что это - лишь авангард, основные силы из танков и пехоты будут позже. А пока они исследуют регион в поисках подходящего места для высадки основных сил. Нам нужна компетентная группа наёмников, чтобы перехватить мехи и остановить вторжение до того, как оно начнется. Если их союзники на планете пришлют какую-либо поддержку, вам надлежит избавиться и от них.

column2: Commander, we were tracking a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} Leopard DropShip through this region when we lost its signal. Orbital scans suggest the ship made landfall here on {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}, probably hoping to go to ground and hide the military lance it was carrying. It would be convenient if that lance were to disappear, and {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} analysts believe they've isolated the area the target lance is trying to hide in.
column3: Командующий {COMMANDER.LastName}, мы вели наблюдение за транспортником класса «Леопард» фракции {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, когда потеряли его сигнал в вашем регионе. При помощи орбитального сканирования нам удалось определить примерное место его посадки, которую он совершил, как полагают аналитики, чтобы спрятать боевой отряд, который был у него на борту. Командование {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} считает, что было бы просто чудесно, если бы данный отряд нигде и никогда бы больше не появился.

You will send a definitive message: Unsanctioned military operations on {TGT_SYSTEM.name} will be eliminated with extreme prejudice. Leave none standing.

И ещё нужно будет прокрутить им эту запись: «Несанкционированные военные операции на {TGT_SYSTEM.name} будут жесточайшим образом пресекаться». Пусть не уцелеет никто.

column2: A lance of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} BattleMechs has been rampaging in {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} territory on {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. They've been razing population centers, burning fields and refineries, looting storage facilities. They're clearly doing everything they can think of to drive our people out. This is terrorism, pure and simple. We need you to find them and destroy them - no escape, and no prisoners.
column3: Копьё боевых мехов {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} бесчинствует на территории {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} на {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. Нам нужно, чтобы вы нашли их и уничтожили - никаких пленных, никаких переговоров.

column2: We have an operation planned to raid a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} logistical base, steal everything that isn't nailed down, and sell it on the black market. There's a missing element in the plan: you. We need you to draw off a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} patrol so that we can move into the base unopposed and load the goods. We figure that you hit the patrol, they call for reinforcements, and then you take those out as well. Then, we sell the stuff and split the take with you.

column2: We just convinced them that they definitely don't need an insurance policy from pirates.

column2: We've been offering our good friends, {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, the opportunity to buy an insurance policy on their 'Mechs. I mean, they're big, complicated pieces of machinery, right? And hardly anyone knows how to fix them? So we're offering to insure them just in case something accidental happens to them. Would you believe they said 'no thanks'? It was a really good offer. We want to show them just how good. We'd like you to cause something accidental to happen to their 'Mechs.

column2: A family associated with {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} has been threatening military action against their {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} neighbors on {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. Neither of us has any legal claim in this system, but as our allied nobles have requested help and protection, we're willing to intervene. We need a deniable force to step in and destroy the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} threat.
column3: Семья, связанная с фракцией {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} угрожала военными действиями {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name}, соседям в системе {TGT_SYSTEM.Name}. Ни у кого из нас нет законных прав посягать на эту систему, но поскольку наши союзные дворяне попросили помощи и защиты, мы желаем вмешаться. Разумеется, мы будем отрицать причастность к любым актам агрессии против {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}.

column2: A {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} leader has fallen behind on payments for their armored vehicles, and our leasing agent has been unable to repossess the heavily armored vehicles. We've decided that sending a more explosive message is the best way to ensure that others do not take future liberties.
column3: У одного из лидеров {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} образовалась задолженность по платежам за бронетехнику, а наш лизинговый агент не сумел экспроприировать тяжелобронированные машины. Мы решили отправить более понятное послание, чтобы дать понять прочим заказчикам, что не стоит допускать подобные вольности в будущем.

column2: That ought to buy our employers enough time to track down the prospector's story.

column2: I'm pulling us out, Commander. Let's not die on an empty rock in space for a wild goose chase.

column2: A prospector with a loose tongue mentioned that he'd located a possible cache of Star League technology on this backwater planet. We've assembled an expert team along with a military force to protect them. They're prepared to investigate, but we've received word that {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} also learned of this cache, and dispatched their own lance to find and secure it. We'd like you to intercept this hostile lance and destroy it while the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} team conducts a thorough search.
column3: Один болтливый старатель рассказал, что обнаружил возможный тайник технологий Звездной Лиги на этой захолустной планете. Мы собрали команду экспертов вместе с вооруженными силами для его защиты. Они готовы к поискам, но мы получили сообщение о том, что {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} также узнали об этом тайнике и отправили своё собственное копьё. Мы хотим, чтобы вы перехватили и уничтожили вражеское копьё, пока команда {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} проводит тщательный поиск.

column2: Secure Borders
column3: Secure Borders

column2: This is the border region our employers are worried about.
column3: This is the border region our employers are worried about.

column2: Orbital surveillance suggests our targets are in this region.

column2: Just the way I like missions to go: simple, with a fat payday at the end.

column2: Commander, {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} surveillance teams have picked up what we believe to be the signature of an active patrol of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} 'Mechs engaging in reconnaissance near the borders of our holdings on this planet. This is technically not a violation of our sovereignty but it's clearly provocative. We need you to send a message, by destroying the patrol 'Mechs. Should you encounter any other {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} units, there will be a bonus for destroying those as well.
column3: Командир, группы наблюдения {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} засекли сигнатуры, как мы полагаем, группы мехов {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, ведущих активную разведку на границах наших владений на этой планете. Технически, это не нарушение суверенитета, но по сути это прямая провокация. Передайте им послание от нас, уничтожив их патруль. Если встретите на пути дополнительные силы {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, то мы заплатим и за их уничтожение.

column2: Many years ago, we fought a lengthy conflict with {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName} here in {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. Recently, however, news has trickled in from a remote region of the planet: enemy forces harrying regional transportation. Eyewitness reports describe very old 'Mechs in colors from the conflict long since ended. You are to show these old MechWarriors that the war is over for them as well.
column3: Много лет назад в {TGT_SYSTEM.name} у нас был длительный конфликт с {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.ShortName}… Однако недавно из отдаленного региона планеты просочилась новость: вражеские силы терроризируют местных, круша их транспорт. Очевидцы говорят об очень старых мехах в раскраске давно окончившегося конфликта. Вы должны показать этим старым воякам, что и для них война уже закончена.

column2: We've got an interesting opportunity for you, Commander. We've recently detected a major engine signature on the planet, probably an assault-class 'Mech. We can't have an assault-class {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} 'Mech that big wandering around loose, and we'd like you to handle it. The interesting part is that we've also detected another assault power-up, and it's a different 'Mech entirely, and it's closing with the target. It's possible you can just swoop in and pick up the pieces. We're prepared to offer generous salvage terms.

column2: After a recent engagement, {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} forces have captured a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} stronghold. This has left the bulk of the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} forces in the field, with nowhere to withdraw to. We'd like you to engage those forces and destroy them in detail. The goal is to break their ability to take the field against us for the forseeable future; that means none of their units should survive.
column3: В результате недавнего столкновения силы {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} захватили крепость {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}. Из-за этого большая часть {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} остались без базы и без возможности отойти на ремонт и перезарядку. Мы хотим, чтобы вы организовали тщательную зачистку и полностью уничтожили их. Цель - сделать так, чтобы они не смогли выступить против нас в обозримом будущем.

column2: We've come across a target of opportunity that we'd like you to take advantage of. There's a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance conducting a long-range patrol, and it's isolated from its supporting forces. If you strike quickly, it should be possible to destroy the lance before {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} command can order reinforcements into the area.
column3: We've come across a target of opportunity that we'd like you to take advantage of. There's a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} lance conducting a long-range patrol, and it's isolated from its supporting forces. column2: Hot Pursuit
column3: Hot Pursuit

column2: We're going in blind, Commander—no time to prepare terrain intel. Meyer, can you see the target lance?
column3: We're going in blind, Commander—no time to prepare terrain intel. Meyer, can you see the target lance?

column2: Affirmative, XO, I've got them in sight. They're right... about...
column3: Affirmative, XO, I've got them in sight. They're right... about...

column2: ...Here.
column3: ...Здесь.

column2: Hit them hard and get the hell out of there, Commander. I have a bad feeling about this one.
column3: Hit them hard and get the hell out of there, Commander. I have a bad feeling about this one.

column2: Speaking of getting the hell out of there: when you're ready to evac, Commander, I'll pick you up here.
column3: Speaking of getting the hell out of there: when you're ready to evac, Commander, I'll pick you up here.

column2: I knew this whole setup was sketchy. Gonna have words with the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} rep about sending us in without complete intel.
column3: I knew this whole setup was sketchy. Gonna have words with the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} rep about sending us in without complete intel.

column2: Primary targets are down, Commander. Get the hell out of there before you're completely overrun.
column3: Primary targets are down, Commander. Get the hell out of there before you're completely overrun.

column2: I'm headed in fast and low, Commander. The LZ is hot, so don't keep me waiting.
column3: I'm headed in fast and low, Commander. The LZ is hot, so don't keep me waiting.

column2: There's the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} bounty hunters, Commander. Still no response, so expect to be fired on.
column3: There's the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} bounty hunters, Commander. Still no response, so expect to be fired on.

column2: Engage, but watch you don't get caught between them and the targets.
column3: Engage, but watch you don't get caught between them and the targets.

column2: All our objectives are complete, cover our withdraw, Commander.
column3: Все наши цели выполнены, прикрывайте наш отход, командир.

column2: Commander, we've got a priority target for you. An elite {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance has just been spotted by our orbital surveillance, out in the open and without any local support. What's more, they've got significant damage from a previous battle. This is an opportunity for us to severely weaken opposition forces on this planet, but we have no forces in range to make the strike. We need you to engage and destroy this lance.
column3: Командир, у нас есть для вас приоритетная цель. Элитное копьё {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} только что было обнаружено нашей орбитальной разведкой, они движутся по открытке, не прячась и похоже без какой-либо поддержки. Более того, они получили значительный урон от предыдущей битвы. Это возможность для нас серьезно ослабить силы противника на этой планете, но у нас нет поблизости достаточных сил, чтобы нанести удар. Нам нужно, чтобы вы вступили в бой и уничтожили это копье.

column2: And here I thought you'd be pleased to see me. You've cost me a fair bit of money lately, and I've decided to put a stop to that. Nothing personal, you understand.

column2: We have a developing situation, Commander, and we need your help to resolve it. One of our minor signals outposts on the planet was attacked and destroyed recently by a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} force, and they're now moving in the open towards a supply depot that we cannot afford to lose. We'd like your team to set down and intercept them; they're very heavily armed, but they're making no real effort to conceal their movement. They should be a relatively simple target.
column3: We have a developing situation, Commander, and we need your help to resolve it. One of our minor signals outposts on the planet was attacked and destroyed recently by a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} force, and they're now moving in the open towards a supply depot that we cannot afford to lose. We'd like your team to set down and intercept them; they're very heavily armed, but they're making no real effort to conceal their movement. They should be a relatively simple target.

column2: I suspect this will be a waste of your time, Commander. I'm perfectly capable of taking care of myself.
column3: I suspect this will be a waste of your time, Commander. I'm perfectly capable of taking care of myself.

column2: We're being paid to accompany you. If there's no fighting, we got paid to stretch our legs and take in the sights.

column2: ... In that case, Commander, we're weapons-hot. Keep that VIP alive.

column2: I'm listening, you know. Don't talk about me like I'm not even here!

column2: A mid-level {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} official has decided to personally patrol a moderately dangerous region of the planet. We've done our best to dissuade her, but she's insistent that she show the people she's willing to take risks on their behalf. Rather than let her stumble around in her family's ancestral Griffin until some opportunistic pirate decides to murder her, we'd like for you to escort her and keep her alive.
column3: Чиновник среднего звена {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} решила лично патрулировать умеренно опасный регион планеты. Мы пытались её отговорить, но она настаивает на том, что готова пойти на риск ради безопасности народа. Мы бы хотели, чтобы вы сопровождали и защищали её на всём пути, иначе она так и будет шататься в своём семейном Гриффине, пока какой-нибудь пират не решит убить ее.

column2: A mid-level {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} official has decided to personally patrol a moderately dangerous region of the planet. We've done our best to dissuade her, but she's insistent that she show the people she's willing to take risks on their behalf. Rather than let her stumble around in her family's ancestral Griffin until some opportunistic pirate decides to murder her, we'd like for you to escort her and keep her alive.
column3: Чиновник среднего звена {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} решила лично патрулировать умеренно опасный регион планеты. Мы сделали всё возможное, чтобы отговорить ее, но она настаивает на том, что готова пойти на риск ради людей. Мы хотели бы, чтобы вы сопроводили её в целости и сохранности, иначе она будет спотыкаться в своем семейном Гриффине, пока какой-нибудь пират не решит убить ее из жалости.

column2: Commander, we've been tracking a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance moving through a contested area on the planet's surface. A few hours ago, our scouts reported another lance, of unknown allegiance, on an interception course. We suspect a fight is brewing, and we'd like you to act as a spoiler. Eliminate the {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance, and the unknown ambushers as well. We don't want to leave any witnesses.
column3: Командир, мы вели наблюдение за копьём {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name}, которое двигалось по оспариваемой территории на поверхности планеты. Несколько часов назад разведка сообщила о ещё одном копье от неизвестной фракции, они идут на перехват первому. Мы подозреваем, что назревает драка и мы хотели бы, чтобы вы вмешались и уничтожили и копьё {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} и неизвестных перехватчиков. Нам не нужны свидетели.

column2: We have a situation here and we'd like your help. We've detected a joint task force of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} and {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units operating openly on the planet. We need to hunt them down and turn them to scrap, but even if we do manage to find them, our own forces aren't up to the task of engaging that many enemies at once. We'd like you to send a lance to accompany our own team; the two of you can then engage the enemy together and negate their numerical advantage.
column3: We have a situation here and we'd like your help. We've detected a joint task force of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} and {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Name} units operating openly on the planet. We need to hunt them down and turn them to scrap, but even if we do manage to find them, our own forces aren't up to the task of engaging that many enemies at once. We'd like you to send a lance to accompany our own team; the two of you can then engage the enemy together and negate their numerical advantage.

column2: We have a situation here and we'd like your help. We've detected a joint task force of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} and {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units operating openly on the planet. We need to hunt them down and turn them to scrap, but even if we do manage to find them, our own forces aren't up to the task of engaging that many enemies at once. We'd like you to send a lance to accompany our own team; the two of you can then engage the enemy together and negate their numerical advantage.
column3: We have a situation here and we'd like your help. We've detected a joint task force of {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} and {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Name} units operating openly on the planet. We need to hunt them down and turn them to scrap, but even if we do manage to find them, our own forces aren't up to the task of engaging that many enemies at once. We'd like you to send a lance to accompany our own team; the two of you can then engage the enemy together and negate their numerical advantage.

column2: We've captured the latest pride and joy of the Capellan Confederation: a Cataphract CTF-IM. Our scientists have been reverse-engineering the monster, but now they say they need real battle data before they can continue. We'd like you to provide that data. We've located a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance to use as a guinea pig. Take the CTF-IM down to the planet and eliminate that lance. Needless to say, we don't have another of these, so it's imperative that you return it intact.
column3: We've captured the latest pride and joy of the Capellan Confederation: a Cataphract CTF-IM. Our scientists have been reverse-engineering the monster, but now they say they need real battle data before they can continue. We'd like you to provide that data. We've located a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} lance to use as a guinea pig. Take the CTF-IM down to the planet and eliminate that lance. Needless to say, we don't have another of these, so it's imperative that you return it intact.

column2: We've captured a rare {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} mech. Our scientists have been reverse-engineering it, but now they say they need real battle data before they can continue. We'd like you to provide that data. We've located a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance to use as a guinea pig. Take the mech down to the planet and eliminate that lance. Needless to say, we don't have another of these, so it's imperative that you return it intact.

We'd like you to provide that data. We've located a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Name} lance to use as a guinea pig. Take the mech down to the planet and eliminate that lance. Needless to say, we don't have another of these, so it's imperative that you return it intact.

column2: Commander, that is the ugliest damn 'Mech I've ever seen. Built like a brick shithouse, though.

column2: Stow it, Yang. We're tracking the target lance in this region, Commander. Move up and put this thing through its paces.

column2: When you're ready to evac, Commander, I'll pick you up here.

column2: Commander, we're planning a joint patrol operation with our allies in a dangerous region of the planet. We're expecting trouble, but these joint exercises are part of a larger diplomatic effort and it's critical that they succeed. We'd like you to provide some additional firepower to ensure that both our lance and our allied lance complete the patrol and evac intact. We're expecting major enemy resistance so plan for a heavy drop.
column3: Командующий {COMMANDER.LastName}, мы планируем провести совместное учебное патрулирование с нашими союзниками в опасном регионе планеты. Несмотря на ожидаемые столкновения, данные учения являются частью дипломатических мер, направленных на улучшения наших отношений с союзниками. И нам крайне важно, чтобы они прошли успешно. Для того, чтобы уменьшить возможное количество несчастных случаев во время этих учений, мы усиляем патруль силами наёмников. В зоне операции ожидается сильное сопротивление противника, так что рекомендуем подготовить тяжёлую технику.

We've picked up a troubling signal which may represent hostile activity, which seems like a good opportunity to send our new defense force out to handle it. Can you bring along an experienced MechWarrior and 'Mech to keep them out of trouble?

column2: We're trying to build a local defense force of MechWarriors here on {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. Our pilots are inexperienced and untested, and we'd like you to help us train them. We've picked up a troubling signal which may represent hostile activity, which seems like a good opportunity to send our new defense force out to handle it. Can you bring along an experienced MechWarrior and 'Mech to keep them out of trouble?

Can you bring along an experienced MechWarrior and 'Mech to keep them out of trouble?

column2: We're trying to build a local defense force of MechWarriors here on {TGT_SYSTEM.name}. Our pilots are inexperienced and untested, and we'd like you to help us train them. We've picked up a troubling signal which may represent hostile activity, which seems like a good opportunity to send our new defense force out to handle it. Can you bring along an experienced MechWarrior and 'Mech to keep them out of trouble?
